node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Vaughn NeVille on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'America's worst mental problem is being told what to think, what to do, who to trust & how to live.'.

node.text: Break the mold, do your own research, trust the people you want to trust, do what you want, live your life on your terms, (just don’t hurt anyone) be free, don’t let others influence you to not questions things. Be proud and never trust the government. #thoughts

node.text: We all have our highs and our lows in life… Some lows burn you into nothing but ashes.  We can either remain in the ash of our new reality, or arise from the ashes like the iconic Phoenix.  Everyday is still a challenge, but I’m choosing to arise, become better and start new.  I still fight my personal internal battles but I’m grateful to work and be better for myself and my children. Thank you all for your continuous prayers, thank you all for you love and support. #thoughts #grateful #homestead #building #barndoninium
